Package com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader

Contains interfaces and implementing classes for creating and managing items from an external data source in the Analysis Repository or an ELP stage.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IClientConnectionBuilder A method for creating an IClientFactory, which enables a bulk data loader to authenticate with and then connect to Intelligence Analysis Platform web services.
IDataLoader A mechanism for creating, updating, deleting, and purging Items from an external data source in an Intelligence Analysis Platform item store.
 

Class Summary
AnalysisRepositoryLoader An implementation of IDataLoader that supports interactions between an external data source and an Analysis Repository.
ElpStageLoader An implementation of IDataLoader that supports interactions between an external data source and an ELP stage.
ItemAndCards A container for information that represents a particular version of an Item and some of the Cards that it contains.
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.loader Description

Contains interfaces and implementing classes for creating and managing items from an external data source in the Analysis Repository or an ELP stage.
